snippet.title: Strife Open Beta: The Trials Begin
snippet.description:
Without a Master Keeper to guard it, the war-ravaged Plane of Strife has opened the gates to the Planes. The time of Trials has come, and Cindara has work to do. 

Strife is the premier second generation MOBA from S2 Games now in Open Beta. Play FREE now at www.strife.com.
